metadata.name: Le Pianiste Virtuose
metadata.description:
A piece dedicated to 1 year of learning piano.

My teacher gave me a book called "The Virtuoso Pianist by Charles-Louis Hanon" - which is a compilation of 60 exercises meant to train the pianist in speed, precision, agility, and strength of all of the fingers.

I practice these exercises on a daily basis using a lacked white Komplete Kontrol S61 midi keyboard which reflects the piano in the jungle.
